.TH "getDC" "1" "" "SequoiaDB User Manuals" ""
.hy
.SH NAME
.PP
getDC \- get data center object
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]db.getDC()\f[]
.SH CATEGORY
.PP
Sdb
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
This function is used to get the data center object.
Through this method, you can obtain an SdbDC object for managing and controlling
the status, location information, and operating modes of the data center.
.SH PARAMETERS
.PP
None
.SH RETURN VALUE
.PP
When the function executes successfully, it returns an SdbDC object.
.PP
When the function fails, an exception will be thrown and an error message will
be printed.
.SH ERRORS
.PP
The common exceptions of \f[C]getDC()\f[] function are as follows:
.PP
