T}
.TE
.PP
When the exception happens, use getLastErrMsg() to get the error message or use
getLastError() to get the error code.
For more details, refer to Troubleshooting.
.SH VERSION
.PP
v3.0 and above
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
\f[B]Example 1:\f[] Get data center object
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc
datacenter1
\f[]
.fi
.PP
\f[B]Example 2:\f[] Get data center object and activate
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc.activate()
\f[]
.fi
.PP
\f[B]Example 3:\f[] Get data center detailed information
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc.getDetail()
